Ombi is your friendly media request tool, automatically syncs with
your media with your media servers!

You'll need to create a channels-dvr user in order to run with the provided init
script:

# groupadd channels-dvr
# useradd -r -d /var/lib/channels-dvr -g channels-dvr channels-dvr

Optionally change these by:

CHANNELS_DVR_USER=user CHANNELS_DVR_GROUP=group ./channels-dvr.Slackbuild

